{"tid":2004744,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人分手後, 會令佢地感到好傷痛, 必定有一個元素","createTime":"2020-05-06T15:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T10:33:42.000Z","uid":89608,"like":25,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a66549e69c43463f809241ba9101ed9938ccd6","tid":2004744,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"女人分手後, 如果提起個戀情, 仲會成日話覺得傷痛, <br />\n會覺得係個沉重經歷, 當中必定包含一個元素<br />\n就係沉重既性關係<br />\n<br />\n如果女人同EX 冇性關係, 佢地分手後, 只會慢慢淡忘, 唔會太上心<br />\n即使個男人係一個衰人, 佢地都唔會覺得提起會係一種傷痛<br />\n<br />\n但如果有沉重性關係, 佢地分手後, 如果個男人係一個衰人, 就會對段戀情記得好深, <br />\n會覺得提起係一種傷痛, 性關係越沉重, 佢地感受既傷會越深<br />\n<br />\n所以, 聽女人點形容佢地同之前衰既EX, 就會知佢地性關係程度"},{"pid":"1108f858f2dbb2816a7ffe0d663148dbaabf07d0","tid":2004744,"uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"何謂沉重性關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f234854d0d91cf7e9a2fb923519adb55f8d0dadb","tid":2004744,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"狗公會上位!!"},{"pid":"eab00622d5c2b0d82d0bf7eb82265d55bdf90b17","tid":2004744,"uid":230662,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"中出過係咪記成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317678ddfdc6adc6216f540a724ac436b1108887","tid":2004744,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eab00622d5c2b0d82d0bf7eb82265d55bdf90b17","tid":2004744,"uid":230662,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"中出過係咪記成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"599d1c523767c55d25c447cbb3962e3339677f6e","tid":2004744,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317678ddfdc6adc6216f540a724ac436b1108887","tid":2004744,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":